import React from 'react';

import {
    Checkbox,
    Divider,
    Grid,
    InputAdornment,
    TextField,
    FormControlLabel,
    FormHelperText,
    RadioGroup,
    Radio,
    Typography,
    Button,
    Stack
} from '@material-ui/core';
// assets
import LockTwoToneIcon from '@material-ui/icons/LockTwoTone';
import LinkTwoToneIcon from '@material-ui/icons/LinkTwoTone';
// project imports
import MainCard from 'ui-component/cards/MainCard';
import InputLabel from 'ui-component/extended/Form/InputLabel';
import { gridSpacing } from 'store/constant';
import AdapterDateFns from '@material-ui/lab/AdapterDateFns';
import LocalizationProvider from '@material-ui/lab/LocalizationProvider';
import DateTimePicker from '@material-ui/lab/DateTimePicker';
import SubCard from 'ui-component/cards/SubCard';

import AnimateButton from 'ui-component/extended/AnimateButton';

// ===========================|| Layouts ||=========================== //
function DailyWorkLoad() {
    const [valueBasic, setValueBasic] = React.useState(new Date());
    return (
        <Grid container spacing={gridSpacing}>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <MainCard title="Client Caseload">
                    <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                        <Grid item xs={8}>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal> Number of Clients</InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={6}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="1" />
                                    <FormHelperText>Please enter your full name</FormHelperText>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal>Total time spent </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={6}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="1" />
                                    <FormHelperText>Total time spent</FormHelperText>
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </MainCard>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <MainCard title="Project Related Clinical Activities ">
                    <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                        Case Management Review Board
                    </Typography>
                    <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Total Time Spent
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="Enter full name" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>
                            <Divider />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                                Administration (e.g., protocol, process, meetings, etc.)
                            </Typography>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Total Time Spent
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>
                            <Divider />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                                Other
                            </Typography>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Detail
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </MainCard>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <MainCard title="Research Related Activities">
                    <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                        Research Meetings
                    </Typography>
                    <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Total Time Spent
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="Enter full name" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>
                            <Divider />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                                Administration (e.g., data gathering, sharing institutional documents, etc.)
                            </Typography>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Total Time Spent
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>
                            <Divider />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                                Other
                            </Typography>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={3} lg={4} sx={{ pt: { xs: 2, sm: '0 !important' } }}>
                                    <InputLabel horizontal sx={{ textAlign: { xs: 'left', sm: 'right' } }}>
                                        Detail
                                    </InputLabel>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </MainCard>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <MainCard title="">
                    <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                        Service Recipient Travel
                    </Typography>
                    <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>
                            <Divider />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} lg={4}>
                            <Typography variant="h5" component="div" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                                Functional Center
                            </Typography>
                            <Grid container spacing={2} alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={9} lg={8}>
                                    <TextField fullWidth placeholder="" />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </MainCard>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <MainCard>
                    <Stack direction="row" justifyContent="flex-end">
                        <AnimateButton>
                            <Button variant="contained" type="submit">
                                Verify & Submit
                            </Button>
                        </AnimateButton>
                    </Stack>
                </MainCard>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    );
}

export default DailyWorkLoad;
